# Visualize empty droplets from CellBender

# Visualize doublets from doublet detection

# Cluster cells at different resolutions

Computing nearest neighbor graph
Computing SNN

# Visualize cells clustered at different resolutions
library(ggplot2)
p=list(length(seq(0.1, .6, by = .05)))
x=1
for (i in seq(0.1, .6, by = .05)) {
  col.name=colnames(swhite_15@meta.data)[match(paste("RNA_snn_scVI_res",i,sep = "."),colnames(swhite_15@meta.data))]
  p[[x]]=UMAPPlot(swhite_15,group.by=col.name,label=TRUE)+ggtitle(col.name)
  x=x+1
}
library(gridExtra)
n <- length(p)
nCol <- floor(sqrt(n))
#do.call("grid.arrange", c(p, ncol=nCol))
# .4 is optimal resolution
